About 011.video web app

011.video is a video editing progressive web App extremely intuitive made for everybody. 80% of the people can use without reading the how-to tutorial. What matters to us is providing a video editor people actually want and can use, not a complex tool box for video designer expert.
Thanks to 011.video you don’t need days of training to make an awesome video. You don’t have to work hours around video timeline or complicated visual effects and so on… to create your own video.
You can mix video, sound, voice, images, drawing, web or PDF external content capture, to make an effective video. Unlike some video editors in the market, you are not restricted by template designs, you can build your video in a freestyle.
